### 5. AI Prompt Tuning (signal_engine.py)

#### [MODIFY] [signal_engine.py](file:///c:/Users/MyBook%20PRO%20K7/Trading%20Bot%20-%20switch/analyzer/signal_engine.py)

Masalah: AI terlalu "scared" di bear market — score 0 untuk SEMUA 30 coins termasuk ETH, SOL, BNB.

Tambahkan instruksi di `SYSTEM_PROMPT`:
```
BEAR MARKET: In bearish regime (F&G<30, composite bearish), SHORT setups are EXPECTED.
Do NOT default score=0 on ALL symbols. Evaluate each independently.
If structure=downtrend + HTF bearish + volume confirms → valid SHORT setup (score 6-8).
Giving score=0 to ALL symbols = lazy analysis. At least 2-3 symbols should have non-zero scores.
```

