```diff
# trade_memory.py (adaptive thresholds)
- if streak <= -3 or weekly_pnl > 5% balance → defensive
+ if streak <= -5 or weekly_pnl > 8% balance → defensive
- if streak <= -2 or recent_wr < 40 → conservative
+ if streak <= -3 or recent_wr < 35 → conservative
